Package com.skobbler.ngx.search

Contains classes needed to make a search (Nearby search , Multistep search).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SKSearchListener Listener for searches.
 

Class Summary
SKAddressSearchSettings Stores input parameters for a multiline address search.
SKMultiStepSearchSettings Stores input parameters for a step by step search.
SKNearbySearchSettings Stores input parameters for a nearby search.
SKOnelineSearchSettings Stores input parameters for a oneline address search.
SKSearchManager Handles search methods
SKSearchResult Class holding information for a search result retrieved by a search.
SKSearchResultParent Stores information about a search result parent.
 

Enum Summary
SKSearchManager.SKListLevel Specifies what list level has to be returned for autocomples search and multiStepSearch.
SKSearchManager.SKSearchMode Search modes
SKSearchResult.SKSearchResultType Describes what the search object represents (Country, state, city, street, POI)
SKSearchStatus Contains information about the status of a search.
 

Package com.skobbler.ngx.search Description

Contains classes needed to make a search (Nearby search , Multistep search).
